\fBWindow options button:\fR
.RS 4
.PP
\fBLMB\fR
.RS 4
Minimize the window (or toggle to the default size)\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBAlt + LMB\fR
.RS 4
Toggle sticky window mode\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBRMB\fR
.RS 4
Set window in "normal" mode (clears stay on top/bottom)\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBMMB\fR
.RS 4
Set window to stay on top\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBAlt + MMB\fR
.RS 4
