.RE
.RE
.sp
.it 1 an-trap
.nr an-no-space-flag 1
.nr an-break-flag 1
.br
.ps +1
\fBArrows button:\fR
.RS 4
.PP
\fBLMB\fR
.RS 4
Move selected window to the left (upper) desktop page\&.
\fBAmiga model\fR: Iconify the window\&.
.RE
.PP
\fBAlt + LMB\fR
.RS 4
